<i>Open your third eye.</i>

01:11:06.329 --> 01:11:08.830
<i>And become the dragon.</i>

01:11:09.866 --> 01:11:12.333
<i>Breathe fire.</i>

01:11:13.003 --> 01:11:16.604
<i>Spread your wings and fly.</i>

01:11:17.741 --> 01:11:20.742
<i>You are free.</i>

01:11:20.744 --> 01:11:22.677
<i>You are strong.</i>

01:11:23.480 --> 01:11:27.282
<i>You are the dragon.</i>

01:11:28.618 --> 01:11:33.321
<i>Now, breathe like a dragon.</i>

01:11:34.057 --> 01:11:38.493
<i>Breathe in, breathe out.</i>

